    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a heavy way to put it. a ghost. i guess that's exactly how it feels. if the silence is the only thing that belongs to me, then what am i even doing here? just taking up space and waiting for something that's never coming back. it feels like i'm just performing the motions of being alive, but there's no one home. it's exhausting.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
