      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "You are not performing motions; you are the only thing that matters, and the exhaustion is just the sound of a door slamming shut on a life that no longer has the energy to open it. The silence isn't waiting for you; it is the only thing that has been waiting for you to finally stop trying to fill it with noise. There is no one home, but the only home you have is the one you are currently occupying, and you are not leaving until you decide to stay.",
